---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Vorion Platform" description="Mission Control for AI Agents - Certify, monitor, and govern autonomous agents across every environment">
  <article class="py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <a href="/projects" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white mb-6">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
          </svg>
          Back to Projects
        </a>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-vorion-500/20 to-accent-cyan/20 border border-vorion-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl">
            🏛️
          </div>
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Vorion Platform</h1>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium rounded-full bg-vorion-500/20 text-vorion-400 border border-vorion-500/30">
                Active Development
              </span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium rounded-full bg-amber-500/20 text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/30">
                README Available
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Mission Control for AI Agents. Vorion certifies agent capabilities, monitors operations in real-time,
          and enforces safety boundaries across every environment. Agents earn clearance through demonstrated performance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Notice -->
      <div class="mb-12 p-6 rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/30">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-amber-400 mb-1">Platform Overview</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-amber-200/70">
              Vorion is the umbrella platform encompassing all governance projects. While the platform
              itself is proprietary, it's built entirely on open source foundations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Overview -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Vorion is Mission Control for autonomous AI. Just as NASA's Mission Control doesn't fly the spacecraft but
          authorizes, monitors, and governs every mission — Vorion certifies agent capabilities, monitors telemetry
          in real-time, and enforces mission rules across every operational environment.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Agents earn clearance through demonstrated performance. New agents start in the simulation environment,
          prove competence through monitored operations, and progressively earn higher clearance levels — from
          ground-restricted (T0) to fully autonomous authority (T7).
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Key Capabilities -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Key Capabilities</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-vorion-500/10 to-transparent border border-vorion-500/20">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🔐</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Zero-Knowledge Audits</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Prove trust claims without revealing sensitive data. Verify scores meet thresholds via ZK proofs (Circom/Groth16).
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/10 to-transparent border border-emerald-500/20">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">🌳</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Merkle Tree Verification</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Optional batch verification with O(log n) proof checks. External anchoring to Ethereum, Polygon, or TSA.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500/10 to-transparent border border-amber-500/20">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">📉</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Clearance Expiry</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              182-day half-life with milestones at 7, 14, 28, 56, 112, and 182 days. Clearance degrades with inactivity — agents must stay active to maintain authorization.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/10 to-transparent border border-cyan-500/20">
            <div class="text-2xl mb-2">📋</div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Flight Recorder</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Full, selective, or ZK audit modes. Every governance decision captured with cryptographic proof — complete transparency or privacy-preserving verification.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Platform Components -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Platform Components</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400">Open Source</span>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">BASIS Standard</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Mission Standards — the foundational specification defining clearance tiers, scoring algorithms, and governance protocols.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400">Open Source</span>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">ATSF Runtime</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Clearance Authority — core libraries implementing trust calculation, clearance decay, Return to Flight recovery, and telemetry.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400">Open Source</span>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Cognigate API</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Mission Gateway — REST/WebSocket API for mission authorization and enforcement at every checkpoint.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded bg-amber-500/20 text-amber-400">Proprietary</span>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">AgentAnchor</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Telemetry dashboard — enterprise visualization, agent management, and compliance reporting.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium rounded bg-amber-500/20 text-amber-400">Proprietary</span>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Aurais</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              AI assistant with integrated governance for end-user interaction.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Architecture Diagram -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Architecture</h2>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-6 font-mono text-sm">
          <pre class="text-slate-400 overflow-x-auto">
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                VORION MISSION CONTROL                     │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                          │
│  ┌──────────────┐    ┌──────────────┐    ┌───────────┐  │
│  │ AgentAnchor  │    │    Aurais    │    │  Learn    │  │
│  │  Dashboard   │    │  Assistant   │    │  Vorion   │  │
│  └──────┬───────┘    └──────┬───────┘    └─────┬─────┘  │
│         │                   │                   │        │
│  ═══════╪═══════════════════╪═══════════════════╪═════  │
│         │            API Layer                  │        │
│  ═══════╪═══════════════════╪═══════════════════╪═════  │
│         │                   │                   │        │
│  ┌──────▼───────────────────▼───────────────────▼────┐  │
│  │          Cognigate — Mission Gateway                │  │
│  │       Mission Authorization & Enforcement          │  │
│  └──────────────────────┬────────────────────────────┘  │
│                         │                                │
│  ┌──────────────────────▼────────────────────────────┐  │
│  │                 ATSF Core Runtime                  │  │
│  │  ┌─────────┐  ┌─────────┐  ┌─────────┐           │  │
│  │  │Clearance│  │ Mission │  │ Flight  │           │  │
│  │  │Authority│  │Briefing │  │Recorder │           │  │
│  │  └─────────┘  └─────────┘  └─────────┘           │  │
│  └───────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │
│                                                          │
│  ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │
│  │             BASIS — Mission Standards               │  │
│  │       8-Tier Clearance Model Specification         │  │
│  └───────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │
│                                                          │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘</pre>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Related -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Explore Components</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/projects/basis" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">
            BASIS Standard
          </a>
          <a href="/projects/atsf" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">
            ATSF Framework
          </a>
          <a href="/projects/cognigate" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Cognigate
          </a>
          <a href="/projects/agentanchor" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">
            AgentAnchor
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
